Installation instructions for zerobot
*************************************

  Dependencies
  ************

  Build-time:
  - libcurl:          multiprotocol file transfer library                   - http://curl.haxx.se/libcurl/
  - expat:            The Expat XML Parser                                  - http://expat.sourceforge.net/
  - SQLite3:          Self-contained, serverless,
                      zero-configuration, transactional SQL database engine - http://www.sqlite.org/
  - HTML Tidy Library                                                       - http://tidy.sourceforge.net/

  Build instructions
  ******************

    $ cd ./zerobot-<version>/
    $ cmake .
    $ make

  Install instructions
  ********************

    Copy zerobot binary to your desired place, e. g. /usr/local/bin/:
    $ cp ./zerobot /usr/local/bin/


P.S.: More advanced use of cmake for installing may follow in the future.
